# Task Breakdown Rule

Write TASK and Context Pack in **Chinese**.

Create TASK documents under `docs/tasks/` using `TASK-TEMPLATE.md`.

Each TASK must:

- Address exactly one focused unit of work
- List done criteria
- Reference parent PLAN and SPEC
- Define files allowed to modify
- Define test commands to run
- Be implementable in a single session

Implement only one TASK at a time unless worktree-based parallel execution is explicitly approved in the Context Pack.
